{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusMenuModelRef\/itemsChanged(position:removed:added:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/dbusmenumodelref\/itemschanged(position:removed:added:)"]}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Requests emission of the [MenuModel](\/\/documentation\/gio\/menumodel\/onitemschanged(flags:handler:) signal on "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"model"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusMenuModelRef","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusMenuModelRef\/MenuModelProtocol-Implementations"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"itemsChanged"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"position","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removed","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"added","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This function should never be called except by "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuModel","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"subclasses.  Any other calls to this function will very likely lead"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"to a violation of the interface of the model."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The implementation should update its internal representation of the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"menu before emitting the signal.  The implementation should further"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"expect to receive queries about the new state of the menu (and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"particularly added menu items) while signal handlers are running.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The implementation must dispatch this call directly from a mainloop"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"entry and not in response to calls – particularly those from the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuModel"},{"type":"text","text":" API.  Said another way: the menu must not change while"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"user code is running without returning to the mainloop.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","extendedModule":"GIO","title":"itemsChanged(position:removed:added:)","externalID":"s:3GIO17MenuModelProtocolPAAE12itemsChanged8position7removed5addedySi_S2itF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO16DBusMenuModelRefV","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"itemsChanged","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"position"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removed","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"added"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}]},"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/DBusMenuModelRef/itemsChanged(position:removed:added:)":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusMenuModelRef\/itemsChanged(position:removed:added:)","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Requests emission of the [MenuModel](\/\/documentation\/gio\/menumodel\/onitemschanged(flags:handler:) signal on "},{"code":"model","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"topic","title":"itemsChanged(position:removed:added:)","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"itemsChanged","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"position","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removed","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"added","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/dbusmenumodelref\/itemschanged(position:removed:added:)"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/DBusMenuModelRef/MenuModelProtocol-Implementations":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"role":"collectionGroup","title":"MenuModelProtocol Implementations","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/dbusmenumodelref\/menumodelprotocol-implementations","kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusMenuModelRef\/MenuModelProtocol-Implementations"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/DBusMenuModelRef":{"abstract":[{"code":"GDBusMenuModel","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is an implementation of [class","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuModel","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":"] that can be","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"used as a proxy for a menu model that is exported over D-Bus with","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"code":"Gio.DBusConnection.export_menu_model","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]."}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/dbusmenumodelref","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"DBusMenuModelRef","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusMenuModelRef","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"DBusMenuModelRef"}],"title":"DBusMenuModelRef"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/MenuModel":{"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MenuModel"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuModel","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/menumodel","title":"MenuModel","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"MenuModel","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GMenuModel"},{"type":"text","text":" represents the contents of a menu — an ordered list of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"menu items. The items are associated with actions, which can be","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"activated through them. Items can be grouped in sections, and may","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"have submenus associated with them. Both items and sections usually","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"have some representation data, such as labels or icons. The type of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the associated action (ie whether it is stateful, and what kind of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"state it has) can influence the representation of the item."}]}}}